X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2007/9/11/21

Conver the uses of PAGE_CACHE_xxx to use page_cache_xxx instead.
Signed-off-by: Christoph Lameter <clameter@sgi.com>
